pageContext.claim: “LOUISIANA! Extreme Democrat John Bel Edwards has sided with Nancy Pelosi and Chuck Schumer to support Sanctuary Cities, High Taxes, and Open Borders. He is crushing Louisiana’s economy and your Second Amendment rights.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is wrong. Louisiana Gov. John Bel Edwards is an especially conservative democrat. VoteSmart, an organization that provides free, factual, unbiased information on candidates, found Edwards supports a slight across the board decline in taxes, enforcement of federal immigration laws and is widely opposed to gun control efforts.
